About Infinity Asset Management Limited

Infinity Asset Management is a Hong Kong based fast growing asset management company. Our company aims to develop external asset management and hedge fund business in Hong Kong. We provide opportunities to candidates with the ambition to obtain experience in the high-net-worth wealth management industry.

JobDescription

1.Responsible for ongoing compliance monitoring 、compliance checkand compliance report preparation for management review on periodic basis；
2.Liaise with asset management department on corporate integrity and regulatory compliance;
3.Assist in fund establishment projects including fund documentation drafting and review, account opening, KYC verification and AML screening;
4.Perform SFC licensing tasks such as individual licence application, notifications and returns submission;
5.Maintain and update internal policies and procedural manuals to ensure compliance with latest regulatory requirements;
6.Prepare responses to SFC’s inquiries, notice or client’s complaints.



The Successful Applicant:

1.Bachelor degree or above in Law, Finance or a related discipline;
2.3 years or above experience in FS compliance, preferably from fund industry;
3.Experience with financial derivatives;
4.Knowledge in SFO and SFC regulations would be an advantage;
5.Strong analytical, problem-solving and communication skills;
6.Good command of verbal and written both English and Chinese (Mandarin and Cantonese);
7.Self-motivated with the ability to multitask in a fast-paced environment.
